{
  "texts": [
    "How consciousness can be sufficiently transferred or even simulated into a foundational LLM remains unknown for the moment and probably the current technological approach itself, presents an insuperable barrier to any progress in this direction.",
    "There exist certain fundamental limitations of the current methods employed to create AI systems, which we explore in detail in the next section.",
    "Capabilities and limitations of current methodsThe impressive performance of LLMs in a wide range of applications has attracted an increasing number of researchers from various scientific fields.",
    "One promising use of LLMs is in drug discovery.",
    "Most of the existing approaches to creating a drug focus solely on recording the underlying chemical patterns and interactions of chemical structures provided by literature data, without connecting to the view of expert scientists in the field."
  ]
}